<p><strong><em>Special Equipment.</em></strong> Talis has +1 scale mail and a wand of winter.</p>

<p><strong><em>Fey Ancestry.</em></strong> Talis has advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic canâ€™t put her to sleep.</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Talis is a 9th-level spellcaster that uses Wisdom as her spellcasting ability (spell save DC 14, +6 to hit with spell attacks). Talis has the following spells prepared from the cleric spell list:</p>

