  </li>
  <li>
    <p>2nd level (3 slots): blindness/deafness, lesser restoration, spiritual weapon (spear)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>3rd level (3 slots): dispel magic, mass healing word, sending</p>
  </li>
