  </li>
  <li>
    <p>5th level (1 slot): insect plague</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong><em>Winter Strike (3/Day).</em></strong> Once per turn, when Talis hits with a melee attack, she can expend a use of this trait to deal an extra 9 (2d8) cold damage.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Spear.</em></strong> Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft. or ranged 20 ft./60 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

